  "original_title": "Increasing productivity and reducing costs with HR Pro SaaS cloud technology",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Increasing productivity and reducing costs with HR Pro SaaS cloud technology",
      "author": "Thilina Walpola",
      "body_lines": [
        "iOM successfully implemented their HRPro HCM cloud suite for one of the largest conglomerates in Philippines. PHINMA has been serving multiple industries in sectors such as Housing, Energy, Finance, as well as Construction. Its subsidiaries Union Galvasteel Corporation (UGC), Philcement Corporation, and Phinma Solar Energy Corporation (Construction Management Group) depend on HRPro a fully-fledged Human Capital Management (HCM) application on a SaaS model to streamline all HR, Time Keeping and Payroll operations in support of rapid business growth.",
        "In the formative years, Payroll Processing and Timekeeping was done manually for most of the PHINMA subsidiaries. The initial phase was to introduce a state-of-the-art HRIS for the PHINMA \u2013 Constructions Materials Group (CMG).",
        "The PHINMA Construction Materials Group (CMG) was created in 2018 to bring together the various PHINMA companies involved in the manufacture and distribution of construction materials and services.",
        "The President and CEO of UGC, Ed Sahagun, passionately driven to improve all the existing operational processes of the PHINMA \u2013 Constructions Materials Group (CMG), mandated their VP Human Resources the Head of MIS to select a suitable HCM Application to be implemented across the Group. The key objectives being the automation of Timekeeping and Payroll whilst ensuring data integrity as well as a system fully compliant with the Data Privacy Act of 2012.",
        "Quickee.lk donates digital teaching system to S. Thomas\u2019 College, Mt Lavinia",
        "Smartphone industry is evolving at a breakneck speed: Yiran An, senior product manager, vivo Imaging Centre",
        "Leave a Reply Cancel replyYour email address will not be published. Required fields are marked *Comment Name *",
        "Save my name, email, and website in this browser for the next time I comment."
